What you need to know:  Okumbi revealed that he left his role to pursue a Uefa 'B' coaching course in Germany for the next six months and added that he will leave the country next weekOkumbi was named Posta Rangers coach in February 2021 after the mailmen sacked Sammy ‘Pamzo’ Omollo and his entire bench due to a string of poor resultsThe mailmen are currently sixth on the log with 25 points from 15 matches with one game at hand